# YouTube Data API v3 key — get one free at https://console.cloud.google.com
# Enable "YouTube Data API v3" then create an API key (unrestricted for local dev)
# Free quota: 10,000 units/day (each channel lookup = 1-2 units)
YOUTUBE_API_KEY=

# Instagram scraping relies on public endpoints — no key needed
# If Instagram blocks requests, users can still enter stats manually
